  <acronym>STAMP</acronym>
  <official_title>Evaluation of the Clinical and Immunological Impact of Two Therapeutic Strategies (Increasing the Infliximab Dose or Introduction of Immunosuppressive Therapy) in Patients Chronic Inflammatory Bowel Diseases in Loss of Response to Infliximab</official_title>
