  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study evaluates 2 therapeutic strategies (increase infliximab dose or add an
      immunosuppressant) in patients with inflammatory bowel disease in loss of response to
      infliximab. Addition of an immunosuppressant may be more efficient at long term and is less
      expensive.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
